We’ve LAUNCHED, not one… not two… but THREE LOVE CORN Multipacks — and they’ve officially hit the Back to School Aisle in Tesco! ✏️📚

Let’s be honest… packing school lunches 5 days a week, 40 weeks a year? It’s a mission. We’re here to make it that little bit easier and a LOT crunchier. 

From packed lunches to park bags to backseat meltdowns — LOVE CORN Multipacks are the crunchy little lifesavers every busy family needs.

You’ll find us in select Tesco stores across the UK.  If you spot us in the wild — please send us a snap. We’re a little starstruck seeing our Multipacks looking this good on shelf! 

Let’s make lunchboxes a little louder this school year ❤️🌽
